OL,3,CBy-election to be called after death
OL,4,Cof Senedd member
OL,6,FA by-election will take place
OL,7,Ffollowing the sudden death of Labour
OL,8,FSenedd member Hefin David last week
OL,10,FThe Senedd's speaker has formally
OL,11,Fdeclared the Caerphilly constituency
OL,12,Fseat vacant, meaning a date for a by-
OL,13,Felection will be confirmed following
OL,14,Fdiscussions with the constituency's
OL,15,Freturning officer.
OL,17,FElin Jones, the speaker or Llywydd,
OL,18,Fissued a statement declaring the seat
OL,19,Fvacant from August 12 in line with the
OL,20,FGovernment of Wales Act 2006 and the
OL,21,FSenedd's rules.
