OL,3,CBy-election to be called after death
OL,4,Cof Senedd member
OL,6,FA by-election must be held within
OL,7,Fthree months of the vacancy occurring
OL,8,Fwhich would make Tuesday, November 11
OL,9,Fthe last possible date.
OL,11,FBy-elections will become a thing of
OL,12,Fthe past from May 2026 when the Senedd
OL,13,Fexpands to 96 members and adopts a
OL,14,Ffully proportional electoral system.
OL,16,FMr David, a 47-year-old father of two,
OL,17,Fwas first elected as an MS for
OL,18,FCaerphilly in 2016 and re-elected in
OL,19,F2021.
