OL,3,CBy-election to be called after death
OL,4,Cof Senedd member
OL,6,FHis partner Vikki Howells is the MS
OL,7,Ffor Cynon Valley and minister for
OL,8,Ffurther and higher education in the
OL,9,FWelsh Government.
OL,11,FGwent Police said they were called to
OL,12,Fa medical emergency just before 7pm on
OL,13,FTuesday 12th August where a 47-year-
OL,14,Fold man was found unresponsive.
OL,16,FParamedics attended and confirmed the
OL,17,Fman had died. His death is not being
OL,18,Ftreated as suspicious.
