OL,3,CBy-election to be called after death
OL,4,Cof Senedd member
OL,6,FIn a statement, Welsh Labour leader
OL,7,Fand First Minister Eluned Morgan paid
OL,8,Ftribute, saying the party is
OL,9,F"extremely saddened by the sudden
OL,10,Fdeath of Hefin."
OL,12,FThe First Minister continued: "Our
OL,13,Fthoughts are with his family at this
OL,14,Fterrible time.
OL,16,F"Hefin was a much-loved member of the
OL,17,FLabour family. He served Caerphilly as
OL,18,Fa councillor and a Member of the
OL,19,FSenedd with pride and passion.
