OL,3,CBy-election to be called after death
OL,4,Cof Senedd member
OL,6,F"He was an outstanding politician,
OL,7,Fwarm and enthusiastic and a great
OL,8,Fcommunicator ` especially on behalf of
OL,9,Fhis constituents. He will be greatly
OL,10,Fmissed."
OL,12,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer also paid
OL,13,Ftribute, describing Hefin David as "a
OL,14,Fpowerful voice for the people of Wales
OL,15,Fand a committed public servant" and
OL,16,Fsaid many are grieving his dedication
OL,17,F"to making sure every person and
OL,18,Fcommunity in Wales had the
OL,19,Fopportunities and support they
OL,20,Fdeserve."
